724237f-a.title: Manhattan: Water Street - Pine Street
724237f-a.text:
(1)
Water Street, west side, north from, but not including Pine Street.
Also shown (across clearance) are Nos. 127-133 Maiden Lane, at, adjoining
and west of the N.W. corner of Water Street. Note the stack of the N.Y.
Steam Co., Plant.
May 30, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, from a different angle, and showing the east side of Water
Street, north to Fulton Street.
May 30, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
The same as No. 1, and shiwing partial demolition of buildings be-
tween Depeyster Street and Maidem Lane.
MN Nj();)  (  April 14, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
